when it was the only character in the parameters list&per.

.br
:li.
If the folder name contains spaces, it is now enclosed
in quotes ("folder name") before being passed as a parameter&per.
This allows Netscape to display these folders also&per.

.br
:li.
Removed faulty information displayed by the install
script&colon. the help file was NEVER copied to \OS2\HELP,
despite the announcement of the install script&per.

.br
:li.
The maximum number of objects in the config folder is
still set to 50; however, instead of crashing, XFolder
will now give you a message, asking you to remove objects&per.

