the parameter list in the program object contains "%"
(like WPS behaviour)&per. This shall henceforth be known
as "Netscape support"&per. ;-) 
.br
:li.
Added online help for XFolder's error messages&per.
This cost me two years of my life&per. 
.br
:li.
Install program improved&colon. replaces previous XFolder
versions; creates more objects than previously, supporting
