                //    The window ID of the tooltip control is ID_XCENTER_TOOLTIP&per.
                // -- WGTF_TOOLTIP_AT_MOUSE&colon. like WGTF_TOOPTIP, but the
                //    tooltip is not centered above the widget, but put
